Mike Huckabee: Twitter Troll Or Presidential Candidate?
In The Young Turks on YouTube by Aaron WysockiOctober 15, 2015Leave a Comment
Mike Huckabee spent last night sending out a series of embarrassing tweets. He said, “Racism exists because we have a sin problem in America, not a skin problem,” among other things. Cenk Uygur and John Iadarola (Think Tank), hosts of the The Young Turks, break it down. Tell us what you think in the comment section below.
“Something Mike Huckabee tweeted during the Democratic debate got a lot of attention on social media tonight.
Huckabee is obviously not a big fan of Bernie Sanders, and tweeted out a few attacks on him tonight:
“I trust @BernieSanders with my tax dollars like I trust a North Korean chef with my labrador! @DemDebate”*